data.description: Motivated Sellers! Sellers offering $5,500 in concessions to use at buyers' discretion! ATTENTION!!! LIMITED TIME BONUS CONCESSION....IF CONTRACT IS EXECUTED BY DECEMBER 31, 2023, LISTING AGENT WILL ADD AN ADDITIONAL $1,500 IN CONCESSIONS!!! THAT IS $7,000 TOTAL IN CONCESSIONS FOR BUYERS TO USE AT THEIR DISCRETION! This home sits on nearly a 1/3 acre corner lot. Current homeowner is a Master Gardener and it shows! With gorgeous plants, flowers, a vegetable garden, and lawn, this yard is a gardener's dream! The pergola-covered patio is a nice place to enjoy company or simply relax after a long day of work. The home itself features high vaulted ceilings throughout the main living areas, as well as a beautifully well-maintained kitchen with a Sub-Zero built-in fridge, wall oven, and stovetop with center griddle. The dining and sitting area is inviting with lots of natural light and a cozy gas fireplace. This home also includes a primary suite with two cedar-lined closets and exterior doors leading to the (included) hot tub. There are two other guest bedrooms and a full bathroom on the main floor. The basement includes a newly renovated full bathroom, bedroom, family room, large laundry room (w/d stay!), and an extra room that has a built-in ventilation system for a workshop space!  The basement also has rough-ins for a wet bar. There is so much to like about this fantastic home. Pics don't do this charming home justice! Schedule a showing to see it in person today!
